text: Coded Cultures is a media arts festival series developed by the Austrian artist collective 5uper.net. The first Coded Cultures focused on the theme 'Decoding Digital Culture' and took place over two weeks in May 2004 at the Museumsquartier in Vienna. ==References== Category:New media art festivals Category:Arts festivals in Austria Category:Recurring events established in 2004 Category:Festivals in Vienna Category:Spring (season) events in Austria
title: Coded Cultures
